Common.Highlight.Common.Text: 6 rear secure car parks on 460sqm site

Common.LongDescription.Common.Text:
CBRE Metro Investments are pleased to present this brilliant office building at 82 Rose Street, Mile End to the market on behalf of our client.

Owner occupiers will love the flexibility that the property offers, with the area being one of the key factors. Mile End is the first suburb west of the CBD meaning it is no more than a few minutes’ drive to West Terrace. More conveniently, the property is a short walk from the Torrensville Shopping Centre and the many surrounding mixed retailers. With the South Road expansion now starting to take shape, areas such as Mile End will continue to see growth and demand in the commercial space.

The subject property is also perfectly positioned with right-in right-out access off South Road meaning there isn’t the constant rush of vehicles passing by, but instead quiet and comfortable use of a great property. Rose Street itself offers a mix of half hour and one-hour street parking suiting businesses that have a lot of walk-in clients. 

- Prime location in western fringe 
- 168sqm of ready-to-go office space
- 6 rear car parks with additional shed storage on 466sqm allotment
- Easy access off South and Henley Beach Roads
- Residential zoning with existing commercial rights (STCC)”
- Top-spec 200/200 internet contract available

This property is for sale via private treaty, seeking offers at $550,000 (plus GST) or above.

For further information please contact exclusive marketing agents CBRE;

Ned Looker – 0448 689 573

Rhyce Scott – 0422 960 585
